behaviors.desc: Defined in `BaseDataletBehaviours.js`. It is the base behavior for all datalets. it contains the main properties common in all visualization : Dataset url, fields and transformed data array

properties.name: dataUrl
properties.desc: It represent the dataset api url

properties.name: fields
properties.desc: It represents one or multiple fields selected by user

properties.name: data
properties.desc: The selected and transformed data you can use in presentation phase

properties.name: factoryImpl
properties.desc: Contructor to create the datalet via javascript
